  "detailed_description": "<br><br><strong>Build your Kingdom in this mix of a City-Builder and Action-RPG!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Loyal companions that help you with everything! </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514980/extras/5e4e04252b20eaf1a030f71e020d536f.poster.avif?t=1641872471\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514980/extras/5e4e04252b20eaf1a030f71e020d536f.webm?t=1641872471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514980/extras/5e4e04252b20eaf1a030f71e020d536f.mp4?t=1641872471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Your villagers follow you and help you with everything! Chop down a tree, and they will chop wood aswell. Attack an enemy, and they will do the same.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build your settlement</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514980/extras/7533dbae92c12fabca206f8ef6700310.poster.avif?t=1641872471\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514980/extras/7533dbae92c12fabca206f8ef6700310.webm?t=1641872471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514980/extras/7533dbae92c12fabca206f8ef6700310.mp4?t=1641872471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Build houses, farms, blacksmiths and many other buildings to create a kingdom to your liking.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Fight off foes and level up your characters</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514980/extras/19dde5cdd6ad0bb3c3638cf399315a67.poster.avif?t=1641872471\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514980/extras/19dde5cdd6ad0bb3c3638cf399315a67.webm?t=1641872471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514980/extras/19dde5cdd6ad0bb3c3638cf399315a67.mp4?t=1641872471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Encounter different enemies on your explorations. Explore a procedurally generated dungeon that is different for every player.<br>Choose how to spend your skill points to become more powerful.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Defend your kingdom at night</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514980/extras/13b9b32083c7742fd24b2a027342e824.poster.avif?t=1641872471\" width=600 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514980/extras/13b9b32083c7742fd24b2a027342e824.webm?t=1641872471\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1514980/extras/13b9b32083c7742fd24b2a027342e824.mp4?t=1641872471\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Build defenses and keep your villagers safe from the attacks of the Corrupted Kingdom.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Smart Companions, that follow what you do<br></li><li> Setup Productions to fulfill your villagers needs<br></li><li> Explore different areas to find more resources and items<br></li><li> Return with your loot and expand your settlement<br></li><li> Relaxed playstyle - no time limits, or overly complicated management stress</li></ul>",
